    <h1>Global Apiculture Directory</h1>
    <p>Discover key associations, research networks, and community groups dedicated to apiculture. Help us improve this living directory by suggesting additions.</p>

    <h2>Featured Global Organisations</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Apimondia</strong> ? International Federation of Beekeepers' Associations; organiser of the World Apiculture Congress.</li>
      <li><strong>COLOSS</strong> ? International network of scientists and experts focused on honey bee health and reducing colony losses.</li>
      <li><strong>International Bee Research Association (IBRA)</strong> ? Charity advancing bee science; publisher of Bee World and Journal of Apicultural Research.</li>
      <li><strong>Food and Agriculture Organization (FAO)</strong> ? UN agency supporting sustainable agriculture and pollinator protection.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>National & Regional Examples</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>American Beekeeping Federation (ABF)</strong> ? USA.</li>
      <li><strong>British Beekeepers Association (BBKA)</strong> ? UK.</li>
      <li><em>+ many more</em> via clubs, university extensions, and research labs worldwide.</li>
    </ul>

